sentences: He came to Abbey Road in 1965 as a tape operator and has since worked with many artists at the studio.
He started his career at Abbey Road as a tea boy, then tape-op, and finally  as a recording engineer, on Pretty Things' S.F. Sorrow, in 1967.
During the early 1980s he pioneered the CD preparation installation in the studio, while working on several outstanding projects.
On 29 August 2013, Mew retired after a 48-year career.
